Title: Magdalene 26 (1)
Plot: After a women running naked along a country way is picked up there are two cases to solve. The first one is to find out how she got there, a complicated task because she suffers from memory loss. The second case goes back quite some years as her DNA was found in a strange cold case with two bodies and a sword.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence, sexual violence & content that may disturb
